      <div class = "text">
        <h2>Diagnostic machine test</h2>
        <p> Some <mark>  PRO WHEELPERS </mark> (technicians and mechanics), are able to carry out a vehicle diagnosis test to detect possible errors or faults in the engine, gearbox, ABS, Airbag and injectors, among other points.
